item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - No Doubt -It's My Life (Party 93.1) Alvarado & Perez Remix from the early 2000
item.description:
I'm looking for the version that this DJ Alvarado had created and used to play on a station that existed back in the early 2000s in Miami called Party 93.1.

It sounds like this a short clip that has been posted on YouTube that can be found under the following title there: No Doubt-It's My Life (Cover, Miami Florida Techno Mix) From WPYM 93.1

If anyone has a good recording, preferably flac (but also mp3 is OK) please post.[/MEDIA]
item.author: miamijunge
